Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界因ZERO創造的奇跡而改變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界因ZERO所展現的行動而重生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 當今世界正邁向新紀元
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.77,0:00:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴隨著無數欲望與情感的波浪 ZERO必須前進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是為了讓時針繼續前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.27,0:00:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和約定的一樣 我一個人來了 到底怎麼回事 傑雷米亞君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說皇女殿下的消息只能告訴我一個人

Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土之味

Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.19,0:02:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑騎士團正朝著鹿兒島沿岸前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是請大家放心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我布里塔尼亞在Knight of One瓦爾德施泰因卿的指揮下…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡已是布里塔尼亞的領土
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.97,0:02:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一兵一卒都別讓他登陸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人中計了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.31,0:02:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天英方向應該會薄弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓登陸部隊咬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍朝著山口進發
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加西亞隊全滅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.47,0:02:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑騎士團這些傢伙 竟投入了這麼多戰力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.39,0:02:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想維持國土絕對防衛線 東中華海戰卻一直被星刻壓著打
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:02:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要驚慌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要守住11區 以奧德修斯殿下為首的皇族都將入侵超合眾國
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其餘的Knight of Rounds也將全體奔赴前線
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.84,0:03:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要解放日本的話 布里塔尼亞的殖民地將一個個奮起反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界地圖將重新繪製
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是天王山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經過去八年了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和娜娜莉被託付給這樞木神社
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 布里塔尼亞小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.50,0:03:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次遇見了朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我救我想救的人 不需要什麼理由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前就是個不懂得變通的傢伙 

Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是正因為如此 你成了我生平第一個朋友


Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 朱雀 我想賭在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如你能夠接受我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不夠打啊 這種程度的祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亞的吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六角突貫陣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提問
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最珍貴的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是生命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星刻大人 左翼崩壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一架突破能力超強的Knightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓英迪拉隊去援護
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左翼全體保持後退 把那台機體孤立起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:04:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修奈澤爾皇子應該還留在東京
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼可擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九州那邊有帝國最強騎士Knight of One在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就留在東京 給他國一種「這只不過是場小紛爭」的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰鬥很快就會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如我沒有判斷錯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在長崎出現的伏兵 被Grausam Valkyrie隊消滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向島根派遣增援部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正面 也讓莫利卿去援護
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡利姆卿後撤 和拉斯科卿匯合重新編隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的攻勢看來快停了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦爾德施泰因大人出擊的話 一口氣解決他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太弱了 以ZERO的作戰而言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Galahad出發
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.39,0:05:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一特裝使用援護裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Galahad出發!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你說好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你能來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亞在特殊情況下 會設置31種路線
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中對關係到皇族的線路尤其鬆懈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你錯了 魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『虧你敢在我面前出現』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是約定?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今誰還會相信你的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼也一個人來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不想再撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像對娜娜莉撒謊的你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一直背叛著我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對學生會的同伴 對娜娜莉也是 就連尤菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎 藤堂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.57,0:06:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的聯絡還沒有來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是Knight of Rounds都出現了 就算是星刻總司令也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能夠相信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自跟Orange、羅洛之流同夥…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得秘密太多了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這之前也秘密派遣木下他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO對目前的我們來說是必須的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是和扇他們說了很多次了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 日本解放以後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇和迪特哈爾特去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想威脅我做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威脅? 不不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想讓你作為黑騎士團的一員 一如既往的工作而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是希望你不要妨礙ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 能代替我的人有一大把…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為你平凡 所以你的存在才有價值
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組織這種東西 成員各個都很耀眼是不能維持的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想確認一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有對尤菲使用GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓她屠殺日本人?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我下令的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼下達這種GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓日本人奮起反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本行政特區成立的話 黑騎士團就崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉之死呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說 夏莉和尤菲都只不過是實現野心的棋子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 所有的罪都在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這和娜娜莉無關
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:08:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬出娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 哥哥為了我 一直扮演著聖誕老人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔的哥哥的外表和ZERO的面具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個才是真正的魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 連這裡都沒來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀沒來這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把洪古的部隊投入左翼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備第二次突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下是指揮官吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擒王來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是戰術的基本…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是Excalibur
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝親自命名的聖劍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我生平第一次向人低頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顧不得體面了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此以外我別無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算GEASS也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 救救娜娜莉吧 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今…你這算啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為你會被原諒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在我只能這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想救娜娜莉 只有靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當我會原諒你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家會原諒你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.33,0:10:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你騙的人 因你而死的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有尤菲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今知道認錯的話 就把尤菲給我復活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的惡意挽救世界給我看看 現在立刻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是創造奇跡的ZERO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是計算和演出的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稱為ZERO的假面只是記號
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是為了撒謊而製造的裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為這種藉口能說得過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是謊言的話 就給我圓謊到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是過去不會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法重新來過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼給我下了「活下去」的GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼




Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對我下的「活下去」的GEASS 扭曲了我的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼對我下那樣的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因涉嫌暗殺克洛維斯殿下而被問罪 你為什麼要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了獲取日本人的信任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒店劫持事件 營救學生會成員又是為了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想利用它讓黑騎士團亮相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這眼神…我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是隱藏秘密接受懲罰的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我加入了布里塔尼亞軍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了補償 為了不讓悲劇重演
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是謊言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修 有一個補償你謊言的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是讓你的謊言成真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你謊稱你是正義的夥伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就成為真正的正義的夥伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把謊言撒到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.49,0:12:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束這場戰爭 如果你是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這是只有ZERO才能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用讓世界變得和平 大家變得幸福的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做的話 我就把娜娜莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出來?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了娜娜莉 再一次與你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你的話 無論什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經知道你的真面目了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 樞木卿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.56,0:13:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從一開始就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你立下大功了 樞木卿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣戰爭就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 你又打算出賣我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你背叛我 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.47,0:13:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你背叛了我!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.33,0:13:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為最近朱雀的樣子有點奇怪 就覺得他是不是有所鬆懈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在學生會室發現的?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 當成寶貝似的放在儲物櫃裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多地方都被撕掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:14:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你… 和恐怖份子關係融洽的情形也許不太好留下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 大家一起麼就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼 那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會流露出這樣的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒見過朱雀像這樣的笑過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是布里塔尼亞人和11區人的混血兒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.87,0:14:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄紅月 選擇斯坦菲爾德這名字的話 就可以很好的生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有這種想法的話 想成為Knight of Rounds也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是想問你有沒有回來這邊的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭德利卿 請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打成這樣 反正是要沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就讓盧西亞諾來有效利用一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.18,0:14:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣解決
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然用同伴的艦艇來做武器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持炮擊 全速後退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:14:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有兩下子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 在這個位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 挺身吃我一劍銜接隨後的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星刻此人 被稱為麒麟兒看來並非浪得虛名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星刻總司令好像負傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大龍膽 後退
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰指揮轉移給參謀長周香凜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到時候嗎 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的真面目居然真的是學生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉爾弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.84,0:15:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇族殺手ZERO的真面目居然是我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是何等的悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇兄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 魯魯修 皇帝陛下那邊由我來周旋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 責罰是不可避免 你的性命我或許還能保住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:15:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想憐憫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 全部是修奈澤爾殿下的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.01,0:16:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是跟著你就能找到ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下已經察覺到了 你和ZERO不尋常的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修 就算是現在我也想扮演你哥哥的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會害你 能信任我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信任你?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 信任你的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常遺憾 皇兄 我已經不再相信任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的友情被出賣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉爾弗德卿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人 你不是Orange
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我只是想拜託你點事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 要我做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 很簡單的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我擺出這個姿勢 那一刻你就把我當作科奈莉婭 然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奈莉婭皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的騎士吉爾弗德 救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你注意到了 吉爾弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉爾弗德卿 你這是幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們才是 居然逮捕皇女 發瘋了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連吉爾弗德卿也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然只有相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇女殿下 暫且先離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 我最初也是最後的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.63,0:17:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直無法相信 吉爾弗德卿居然會叛變
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.24,0:17:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.70,0:17:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡待機
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.39,0:17:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 修奈澤爾殿下的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.66,0:17:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說ZERO出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也沒被通知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像得知什麼非常糟糕的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想確認一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有對尤菲使用GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的話 應該清楚吉爾弗德卿叛變的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及你曾經在神根島採取的行動的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是應該追擊ZERO嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們缺少非常重要的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所知道的情報…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wired-C 確認反應
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取得同步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ragnarok Backup 進行復位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉爾弗德 就這樣前往東京租界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.74,0:18:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樞木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.51,0:18:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本人?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名譽布里塔尼亞人?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Knight of Seven
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是樞木玄武首相的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修的朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:19:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲米婭的騎士?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不願意說的話 我們就只有投身不公平的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓這悲哀的連鎖持續到何時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,租界結構的修改已經完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會像以前那樣讓ZERO破壞這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到了 是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎 蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備狙擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把Vincent打下來也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們以為我在租界就只是當個學生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京租界 現在就讓你停止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Energy Filler…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gefion Disturber嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 關於這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視機前的各位觀眾 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播放室的電源好像斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 條件就緒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤堂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.86,0:20:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七號作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑鳩浮上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑鳩浮上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦隊各戰鬥部隊 隨時準備浮上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇 現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦隊就這樣穿過東京灣 突入東京租界 和ZERO會合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各員 戰鬥配置
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.09,0:20:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的忠義 為了魯魯修殿下和娜娜莉殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.77,0:20:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 黑騎士團突入東京灣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦爾德施泰因卿 派我和直屬的Grausam Valkyrie隊去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去東京租界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼想建功嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我只是想破壞而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛 你那如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 作戰已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:21:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就去迎接娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 拜託了 羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友情什麼的是靠不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜 無情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不將自我化為完全體 就不能把娜娜莉奪回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修 從克洛維斯那時我就覺得事有蹊蹺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.08,0:21:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我已經理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.06,0:21:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我理解並接受了 現在所有的牌都在我的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 一開始就告訴修奈澤爾殿下的話 就不會引發這樣的戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是Knight of Rounds 我不能處罰你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心理的罪惡就自己去尋找答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界不會只對你一個人溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:21:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有坐上去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:21:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐上這裝著Freyja的Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用Freyja把魯魯修…

Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你真敢幹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.40,0:23:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,欺騙我 踐踏我的尊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.41,0:23:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,鄙視我的人們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.10,0:23:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定會贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.62,0:23:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我會贏過修奈澤爾 朱雀給你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.79,0:23:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你們把我設為目標而行動著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.04,0:23:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 來迎接我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.61,0:23:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我來破壞 讓我給你們看看絕望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.02,0:24:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,然後我再去迎接娜娜莉 解救卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,最後笑的會是我
